@context: Automation Practice Gauntlet (testautomationpractice.blogspot.com). Includes text inputs, radio/checkboxes, dropdowns, date pickers, drag-and-drop, dynamic tables with pagination, and Shadow DOM.
@blueprint: complex_ui_full_inspection

# 🐾 THE MEGA HUNT: Ultimate Automation Challenge
# Validation of all possible element types on a single page.

1. NAVIGATE to https://testautomationpractice.blogspot.com/

# ── Text inputs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
2. Fill "Name" field with "Mega Manul"
3. Fill "Email" field with "mega@manul.ai"
4. Fill "Phone" field with "9876543210"
5. Fill "Address" textarea with "Selenium Avenue, 42, AI City"
6. VERIFY that 'Mega Manul' is present.

# ── Radio button & Checkboxes ──────────────────────────────────────
7. Click the radio button for "Male"
8. VERIFY that 'Male' is checked.
9. Click the checkbox for "Monday"
10. VERIFY that 'Monday' is checked.
11. Click the checkbox for "Tuesday"
12. VERIFY that 'Tuesday' is checked.
13. Click the checkbox for "Thursday"
14. VERIFY that 'Thursday' is checked.

# ── Selection Lists ────────────────────────────────────────────────
15. Select "Japan" from the "Country" dropdown
16. VERIFY that 'Japan' is present.
17. Select "Blue" from the "Colors" list

# ── Date Picker & Interactive Buttons ──────────────────────────────
18. Fill "Date Picker 1" field with "12/31/2026"
19. SCROLL DOWN
20. Click the "START" button
21. DOUBLE CLICK the button that says "Copy Text"
22. VERIFY that 'Hello World!' is present.

# ── Drag and Drop ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
23. Drag the element "Drag me to my target" and drop it into "Drop here"
24. VERIFY that 'Dropped!' is present.

# ── Data extraction from web table ─────────────────────────────────
25. SCROLL DOWN
26. EXTRACT the CPU of "Chrome" into {chrome_cpu}
27. EXTRACT the CPU of "Firefox" into {firefox_cpu}
28. EXTRACT the Price of "Master In Selenium" into {book_price}
29. EXTRACT the Price of "Selenium" into {selenium_price}
30. VERIFY that '3000' is present.

# ── Pagination Table ────────────────────────────────────────────────
31. SCROLL DOWN
32. Click on page "2" in the pagination list
33. Select the checkbox for the product with ID "7"
34. Click on page "4" in the pagination list
35. Select the checkbox for the product with ID "17"

# ── Scrolling Dropdown (Complex React/JS component) ────────────────
36. SCROLL DOWN
37. Click the "Scrolling DropDown" input field
38. SCROLL DOWN inside the list
39. Click "Item 100"
40. VERIFY that 'Item 100' is present.

# ── Shadow DOM (Deep Element Access) ───────────────────────────────
41. SCROLL DOWN to the very bottom
42. Locate the text input inside the Shadow Root
43. Type "Shadow Boss" into that field
44. VERIFY that 'Shadow Boss' is present.

# ── Final Mission Validation ───────────────────────────────────────
45. VERIFY that "Mega Manul" and "Japan" and "Dropped!" and "Item 100" and "Shadow Boss" are present.
46. DONE.